  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Here's what you'll go bananas for:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore five diverse and unique biomes </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete engaging objectives and collect mojos </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover mysteries and enjoy a compelling story </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relaxing yet challenging time management gameplay </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden critters in every level </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adapt to changing landscapes and biomes</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set off on an adventure with a troop of resilient monkeys, shipwrecked by a storm and stranded on a mysterious island.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Chimp Quest: Spirit Isle! It’s a point-and-click time management game that feels like those nostalgic gems we used to play, perfect for monkeying around and losing yourself in an exciting journey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/621eb784a3b775512dcecdc61a5d8993.poster.avif?t=1729643539\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/621eb784a3b775512dcecdc61a5d8993.webm?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/621eb784a3b775512dcecdc61a5d8993.mp4?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Chimp Quest: Spirit Isle, you’ll join these determined monkeys as they explore the island's depths, uncover ancient ruins, and meet other monkeys each with their own unique stories. Your goal? To collect mystical mojos, appease the island's spirits, and help transform this uncharted land into a new home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/31b434497cd4e23578f475d0dfc03d1e.poster.avif?t=1729643539\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/31b434497cd4e23578f475d0dfc03d1e.webm?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/31b434497cd4e23578f475d0dfc03d1e.mp4?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you help the monkeys find their new home and bring harmony to Spirit Isle? Play Chimp Quest: Spirit Isle now and start your adventure!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set off on an adventure with a troop of resilient monkeys, shipwrecked by a storm and stranded on a mysterious island.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Chimp Quest: Spirit Isle! It’s a point-and-click time management game that feels like those nostalgic gems we used to play, perfect for monkeying around and losing yourself in an exciting journey. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/621eb784a3b775512dcecdc61a5d8993.poster.avif?t=1729643539\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/621eb784a3b775512dcecdc61a5d8993.webm?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/621eb784a3b775512dcecdc61a5d8993.mp4?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Chimp Quest: Spirit Isle, you’ll join these determined monkeys as they explore the island's depths, uncover ancient ruins, and meet other monkeys each with their own unique stories. Your goal? To collect mystical mojos, appease the island's spirits, and help transform this uncharted land into a new home. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/31b434497cd4e23578f475d0dfc03d1e.poster.avif?t=1729643539\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/31b434497cd4e23578f475d0dfc03d1e.webm?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463700/extras/31b434497cd4e23578f475d0dfc03d1e.mp4?t=1729643539\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you help the monkeys find their new home and bring harmony to Spirit Isle? Play Chimp Quest: Spirit Isle now and start your adventure!</p>",
